      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">The Personal AI Revolution Is Coming. Nobody's Building the Knowledge Layer.</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">HTTP moved documents between computers. OTP moves operational intelligence between AI systems. The knowledge transfer layer for the personal AI era does not exist yet.</p>
